data.description: Updates, space, & location! In the beautiful Olde Forest neighborhood, this house boasts recently refinished hardwoods (2021) throughout main living areas, updated light fixtures, & tons of natural light everywhere you turn. You’re greeted w/ a grand dbl foyer, a den to the right w/ gas log FP. Large dining room. Kitchen offers tons of storage, dbl oven, SS appliances, desk area, & dbl door pantry. Oversized living room w/ gas logs. Enjoy every season in the vaulted all season room. Step out onto the 17x19 privacy deck. Take a stroll down the stairs to the brick laid Brazilian BBQ! An outdoor, full functioning kitchen, complete w/ a sink, wood burning grill, 2 burners & seating around a fire pit. Bed 2 located on main level w/ full updated bath. Primary suite offers vaulted ceilings, double sided FP, sitting room, & private views. Primary bath includes double vanities w/ jetted garden tub, separate shower, & giant closet. 3 other spacious bedrooms upstairs.
